{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775858647729,"sessionID":"ses_28693a447ffe325dW9hzDqbxCM","part":{"id":"prt_d796c7de60016yiERhvmbracNS","messageID":"msg_d796c71bb001aeBUxS5WftEBXZ","sessionID":"ses_28693a447ffe325dW9hzDqbxCM","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_be494f375fb240a590c97d32","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/agentd  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** S  \n6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Implementation Tasks\n11: \n12: ### Phase 1: Package Structure & Constants\n13: \n14: - [ ] **T001** Create `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` with:\n15:   - Package declaration `package agentd`\n16:   - Import statements for:\n17:     - `time`, `context`\n18:     - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors`\n19:     - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime`\n20:     - `k8s.io/klog/v2`\n21:     - `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` (sandboxv1alpha1)\n22:     - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client`\n23:     - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/controller/controllerutil`\n24:     - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager`\n25:   - Define constant `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`\n26:   - Define constant `lastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"` (local reference to workloadmanager constant)\n27: \n28: ### Phase 2: Reconciler Implementation\n29: \n30: - [ ] **T010** Implement `Reconciler` struct in `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go`:\n31:   ```go\n32:   type Reconciler struct {\n33:       client.Client\n34:       Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n35:   }\n36:   ```\n37: \n38: - [ ] **T011** Implement `Reconcile` method with exact algorithm:\n39:   1. Get Sandbox object by namespaced name\n40:   2. If NotFound, return empty result\n41:   3. If other error, return error\n42:   4. Read `last-activity-time` annotation\n43:   5. If annotation exists and non-empty:\n44:      - Parse RFC3339 timestamp\n45:      - If parse error, return RequeueAfter: 30s with error\n46:      - Compute expirationTime = lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)\n47:      - If now After expirationTime: delete Sandbox, ignore NotFound errors\n48:      - Else: return RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)\n49:   6. Return empty result\n50: \n51: - [ ] **T012** Implement `SetupWithManager` function:\n52:   ```go\n53:   func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n54:       return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n55:           For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n56:           Complete(r)\n57:   }\n58:   ```\n59: \n60: - [ ] **T013** Add necessary controller-runtime imports (`sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime`)\n61: \n62: ### Phase 3: Binary Entry Point\n63: \n64: - [ ] **T020** Create `cmd/agentd/main.go` with:\n65:   - Package main\n66:   - Import statements:\n67:     - `runtime` (k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime)\n68:     - `utilruntime` (k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/runtime)\n69:     - `ctrl \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\"`\n70:     - `metricsserver \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/metrics/server\"`\n71:     - Core Kubernetes types via k8s.io/api (for scheme)\n72:     - sandboxv1alpha1 (for scheme)\n73:     - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\n74:   - init() function to register schemes:\n75:     ```go\n76:     var schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()\n77: \n78:     func init() {\n79:         utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n80:         utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n81:     }\n82:     ```\n83:   - Main function with manager setup:\n84:     ```go\n85:     mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n86:         Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n87:         Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n88:         HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\",\n89:     })\n90:     ```\n91:   - Register controller:\n92:     ```go\n93:     err = ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n94:         For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n95:         Complete(&agentd.Reconciler{\n96:             Client: mgr.GetClient(),\n97:             Scheme: mgr.GetScheme(),\n98:         })\n99:     ```\n100:   - Start manager: `mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())`\n101: \n102: ### Phase 4: Unit Tests\n103: \n104: - [ ] **T030** Create `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go`:\n105:   - Test Reconcile returns nil when Sandbox not found\n106:   - Test Reconcile skips deletion when no annotation\n107:   - Test Reconcile deletes when expired (last-activity-time > 15 min ago)\n108:   - Test Reconcile requeues with correct duration when not expired\n109:   - Test Reconcile requeues 30s on parse error\n110:   - Test Reconcile handles NotFound on delete gracefully\n111: \n112: - [ ] **T031** Add table-driven tests for time parsing edge cases\n113: \n114: ### Phase 5: Build & Verify\n115: \n116: - [ ] **T040** Run `go mod tidy` - ensure dependencies resolved\n117: \n118: - [ ] **T041** Run `go build ./cmd/agentd` - verify build succeeds\n119: \n120: - [ ] **T042** Run `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` - verify all unit tests pass\n121: \n122: - [ ] **T043** Run `go vet ./pkg/agentd/...` - verify no vet errors\n123: \n124: ---\n125: \n126: ## Dependencies\n127: \n128: - **T001**: None (new package)\n129: - **T010**: T001\n130: - **T011**: T010\n131: - **T012**: T010\n132: - **T013**: T010\n133: - **T020**: T012 (requires reconciler import)\n134: - **T030**: T011 (tests Reconcile method)\n135: - **T031**: T030\n136: - **T040**: All implementation tasks\n137: - **T041**: T020\n138: - **T042**: T030, T031\n139: - **T043**: T041\n140: \n141: ---\n142: \n143: ## Configuration Variables\n144: \n145: | Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n146: |----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n147: | None | - | - | No runtime configuration required - uses fixed 15 minute timeout |\n148: \n149: ---\n150: \n151: ## Architecture Notes\n152: \n153: ### Data Structures\n154: \n155: ```go\n156: // pkg/agentd/reconciler.go\n157: const SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n158: const lastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"\n159: \n160: type Reconciler struct {\n161:     client.Client\n162:     *runtime.Scheme\n163: }\n164: ```\n165: \n166: ### Constants\n167: \n168: | Constant | Value | Description |\n169: |----------|-------|-------------|\n170: | SessionExpirationTimeout | 15 * time.Minute | Idle session expiration threshold |\n171: | lastActivityAnnotationKey | \"last-activity-time\" | Annotation key for last activity timestamp |\n172: \n173: ### Key Behaviors\n174: \n175: 1. **Reconcile flow**:\n176:    - Get Sandbox → NotFound? → return nil\n177:    - Read `last-activity-time` annotation → missing/empty? → return nil\n178:    - Parse timestamp → error? → return RequeueAfter(30s) with error\n179:    - Compute expiration → expired? → Delete, ignore NotFound\n180:    - Not expired → return RequeueAfter(time.Until(expirationTime))\n181: \n182: 2. **Idempotency**: Delete NotFound = success\n183: \n184: 3. **Manager config**: Metrics disabled, health probe disabled\n185: \n186: ---\n187: \n188: ## References\n189: \n190: - Design Doc: `idle-cleanup/design.md`\n191: - Spec Doc: `idle-cleanup/spec.md`\n192: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md`\n193: - Workload Manager (annotation key): `pkg/workloadmanager/gc.go:666`\n194: - Sandbox API: `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`\n\n(End of file - total 194 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/agentd  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: Package Structure & Constants\n\n- [ ] **T001** Create `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` with:\n  - Package declaration `package agentd`\n  - Import statements for:\n    - `time`, `context`\n    - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors`\n    - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime`\n    - `k8s.io/klog/v2`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775858647702,"end":1775858647726}}}}
